				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The Glacier Bear does spawn every 24 hours NO MATTER WHAT, ph killed or not.  Ther are wandering IB skellies that are placeholders but the bear WILL spawn every 24 hours without killing the ph's.<BR>
<BR>
The bear was simple to kill Every time I killed him, which has been numerous times, he was a lvl 28.  I started camping him at 29 and once you figure out he is cold resistant, he is simple.<BR>
You just have to use the old root Dot root Dot and then slow him at half power and beat him dead<BR>
<BR>
Every time I killed him, total of 7 now, he has dropped both the icon and the glacier bear pelt.<BR>
<BR>
It is not that bad of a quest for either shaman or cleric, just have to do a little investigation first.
