	</tr>
	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				****IMPORTANT PLEASE READ*****<BR>
<BR>
This glacial bear has got to be THE SINGLE MOST STUPID camp in EQ. <BR>
(sorry I'm a VERY frustrated cleric on the Drinal server of the 47th level)  I have camped this spawn several times...once over 15hours straight with NO BEAR  SPAWNING the ENTIRE time!!!  Last eve...m'hubby and I (a level 45 Wizzard) went to see if he was up again.  I was off trying to find another icon that spawns in the bottom of the river nearby (for an unrelated quest) when lo, and behold!  The elusive bear!!!  I raced quickly to aid m'hubby in killing the dreaded thing but was so far south of the cave entrance he had to follow it.  He followed it for a bit until he was trapped between Lich and the bear.  To avoid Lich he had to let the bear wander off and we never saw him again that eve.  Guess the thing just DESPAWNED or something! =(  Completely frustrated we decided to call it a night and try again in the morning...<BR>
<BR>
Sleepily sitting at the computer, I searched the web here for info on Lich as I waited to see if the bear would show his white-self this day.  OMG!!!  Could it be???  &quot;Glacial Bear&quot;  <BR>
<BR>
WOOHOOO I've been waiting SOOOOOO long...<BR>
<BR>
He conned green to me so I left m'hubby's char logged off (shouldn't need his help to kill it!)  and proceeded to commence firing!  With little effort (and little dmg done to me--I wasn't even BUFFED!)  the bear was DEAD!!!  <BR>
<BR>
Wow!! Shaking with glee, my trembling hand grabbed the mouse and I clicked <BR>
on the dead corpse to loot it...NO ICON!?!?!?   WHAT???  ANOTHER 8 hours or so of waiting NOW?!??? *grumble* <BR>
<BR>
Not ONE post has mentioned that you get EITHER the icon OR the pelt...what's <BR>
up with THAT???  *sigh* <BR>
<BR>
Just thought I'd pass along some info in case any of you all would like the icon, <BR>
this shield seems TOTALLY not worth the time and effort.<BR>
<BR>
Thank you for letting me rant a bit...and I DO hope this info helps someone out there!<BR>
<BR>
*hugs*<BR>
<BR>
Aalyve Wyyre<BR>
Cleric of the Lost Moon<BR>
Drinal Server
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
